<text top="2520" left="841" width="344" height="43" font="font5" id="p1_t119" reading_order_no="118" segment_no="17" tag_type="text">bunch  of  iffy  loans  and  sell </text>
<text top="2565" left="840" width="348" height="43" font="font5" id="p1_t120" reading_order_no="119" segment_no="17" tag_type="text">them  to  investment  banks, </text>
