<text top="1737" left="1293" width="370" height="42" font="font13" id="p1_t142" reading_order_no="141" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">“lunacy.”  Michael  Burry,  who </text>
<text top="1785" left="1293" width="390" height="41" font="font12" id="p1_t143" reading_order_no="142" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">runs  hedge  fund  Scion  Capital </text>
