<text top="2015" left="1293" width="353" height="41" font="font12" id="p1_t148" reading_order_no="147" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">mortgages,  says his  thesis </text>
<text top="2062" left="1293" width="381" height="41" font="font12" id="p1_t149" reading_order_no="148" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">was  that  “the  rating  agencies </text>
